name: THE MANSION
description: As the night gets longer and longer, the alcohol starts to take control. Your vision blurs. There's not much left in terms of conversation. Parties like this are new to you but you try to fit in. Drink a bit too much and this is how it ends up. Oh well. You won't remember in the morning anyway. 4032x2268 JPEG Created by: @ErikJohnsonDP
